You can literally take
any movie scene you want,

00:53:36.810 --> 00:53:38.580
add music to it, and
watch how it changes.

00:53:38.580 --> 00:53:39.371
Watch what happens.

00:53:39.371 --> 00:53:41.400
I had one group where
somebody shouted out

00:53:41.400 --> 00:53:43.740
last scene of "Casablanca,"
and somebody shouted out

00:53:43.740 --> 00:53:45.822
"We Are The Champions" by Queen.

00:53:45.822 --> 00:53:47.030
And they thought they had me.

00:53:47.030 --> 00:53:48.180
They thought they'd nailed me.

00:53:48.180 --> 00:53:49.230
And I was a little
nervous, I was

00:53:49.230 --> 00:53:50.550
like, I don't know how
this is going to go.

00:53:50.550 --> 00:53:53.100
So we go to YouTube, we
bring up the "Casablanca,"

00:53:53.100 --> 00:53:53.862
put it on mute.

00:53:53.862 --> 00:53:55.320
We bring up "We
Are The Champions,"

00:53:55.320 --> 00:53:58.230
turn it on, start the two
of them, we start watching.

00:53:58.230 --> 00:54:00.850
And it's shocking how
it starts to line up.

00:54:00.850 --> 00:54:02.340
And as the plane
starts to take off

00:54:02.340 --> 00:54:05.370
and Elsa's is being taken away,
the music is crescendoing,

00:54:05.370 --> 00:54:08.980
and Freddie Mercury is
going, "We are the champ--"

00:54:08.980 --> 00:54:10.970
and you like, oh my
god, it's so moving.

00:54:10.970 --> 00:54:13.410
And it's totally random, and--

00:54:13.410 --> 00:54:14.787
play this game.

00:54:14.787 --> 00:54:15.870
Literally, play this game.

00:54:15.870 --> 00:54:18.780
And it sounds silly,
but it's amazing

00:54:18.780 --> 00:54:21.594
how it sets you
up for then being

00:54:21.594 --> 00:54:23.760
able to connect to things
you ordinarily would never

00:54:23.760 --> 00:54:25.380
think would work.

00:54:25.380 --> 00:54:28.200
And that's where those
breakthroughs come from.

00:54:28.200 --> 00:54:30.930
So there's play involved,
there's a craft involved,

00:54:30.930 --> 00:54:32.400
there's practice involved.

00:54:32.400 --> 00:54:33.750
There are these tools, it's--

00:54:33.750 --> 00:54:36.900
but it's not something in
theory, it's something you do.

00:54:36.900 --> 00:54:39.270
It's a way you are in the world.

00:54:39.270 --> 00:54:42.480
And so you have the ability.

00:54:42.480 --> 00:54:43.830
You have the brain for this.

00:54:43.830 --> 00:54:47.250
You have all the parts
for it, everybody does.

00:54:47.250 --> 00:54:49.610
We just have to use
them, practice with them,

00:54:49.610 --> 00:54:51.360
and get comfortable with them.

00:54:51.360 --> 00:54:53.880
And that's why we
wrote the book.

00:54:53.880 --> 00:54:55.870
See, that's nicer.

00:54:55.870 --> 00:54:57.080
Thank you, everybody.

00:54:57.080 --> 00:54:59.830
[APPLAUSE]

